[Episode 4] @mark_zona_fishing and @kevinvandamfishing are reunited on the water for the first time in years to put on a beatdown of epic proportions on Lake St. Clair 💥 

Follow @greghackneyfishing's journey as he tackles one of the greatest bass fishing lakes in the nation and learn how he got into the sport we all love.

What's something new you learned from this episode? How are we liking the new season?

#Lews #LewsFishing #TeamLews #StrikeKing #StrikeKingLures #TieOne #KingsOfBass #bassfishing #outdoors #fishingislife

node.text:
Who's ready for a new episode of KINGS OF BASS?! Air date is 𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐉𝐮𝐧𝐞 𝟐𝟖 𝐚𝐭 𝟕𝐩𝐦 𝐄𝐓 𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐞𝐰'𝐬 𝐈𝐆𝐓𝐕 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐓𝐮𝐛𝐞.

Reunited on the water for the first time in years. @mark_zona_fishing phones a friend and puts on a beatdown of epic proportions with @kevinvandamfishing on Lake St. Clair! Go behind the scenes and see how Z prepares to film a fishing show and hear how bass fishing has changed his life.

@greghackneyfishing continues his quest to qualify for the #BassmasterClassic at Lake Fork. Follow his journey as he tackles one of the greatest bass fishing lakes and learn how he got into the sport we all love.

#Lews #TeamLews #LewsFishing #StrikeKing #KingsOfBass

Double tap if you'll be watching and tag a friend who hasn't watched KINGS OF BASS yet!

Episode 4 features @greghackneyfishing, @mark_zona_fishing and a special guest appearance. Any guesses?? 🤔

#Lews #TeamLews #KingsOfBass #StrikeKing #bassfishing #Bassmaster #bassnation #fishingvideos

node.text:
[𝐍𝐄𝐖 𝐄𝐏𝐈𝐒𝐎𝐃𝐄] 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐁𝐚𝐬𝐬: 𝐄𝐩𝐢𝐬𝐨𝐝𝐞 𝟒
Air Date: Monday, June 28 at 7pm ET
IGTV + YouTube Premiere
 
For @mark_zona_fishing producing fishing shows are the equivalent of fishing a tournament, but the entry fee and stakes are much higher. We go behind the scenes as he prepares to film three back-to-back episodes of Pro Team Journal on Lake St. Clair. See the passion, dedication, and grind that Mark Zona puts into every single show.

@greghackneyfishing goes back to his roots in Episode 4. Watch along as he takes us through why he chose the career path of being a professional angler and what it takes to succeed at this level. 

#KingsOfBass #Lews #LewsFishing #TeamLews #MarkZona #GregHackney

node.text:
Here's a look at the NEW Mark Zona Team Lew's Signature Series of rods. (Available Fall 2021) 

“With my style of spinning, sensitivity is key. I have no patience for missing even the slightest strike. This was my most critical request for my friends at Lew’s - build a rod with exceptional sensitivity - and Team Lew’s delivered,” - @mark_zona_fishing host of ZONA's Awesome Fishing Show! and The Bassmasters on FS1.

Details at the link in our bio 💥

#TeamLews #Lews #LewsFishing #LewsSignatureSeries #bassfishing #fishingrods

node.text:
Here's a look at the Team Lew's Signature Series of rods. Designed by 5 of the most credible bass tournament fishermen in the world, these series of technique-specific rods will cater to any angling style and preference.

There's nowhere @andymontgomeryfishing can't place a bait. Andy's signature series features 3 rods built to flip, pitch and skip your way to big bags of fish. Which version are you eyeing up?

Coming Fall 2021.

#TeamLews #LewsFishing #LewsSignatureSeries #fishingrods #Lews #bassfishing

node.title: Team Lew's Signature Series Rods | Andy Montgomery

node.text:
@kevinvandamfishing is unarguably one of the greatest bass anglers of our time. Hot off his first @majorleaguefishingofficial Bass Pro Tour victory on Lake Chickamauga, we're proud to introduce Kevin's all new Team Lew's Signature Series of rods.

When the GOAT speaks - we listen. For the past year, KVD has been diligently designing his Signature Series with the product development team at Lew's. His craft demands perfection and we're proud of the collection of KVD's technique-specific rods we've put together. 

Coming soon to lews.com. Stay tuned for more details!

#Lews #TeamLews #LewsSignatureSeries #LewsFishing #bassfishing #BassProTour #MajorLeagueFishing #MLF #KVD
